**************************************** Case 2 Delete Dist Plans ****************************************
## case #2
## delete分布式计划，delete现在只支持单表的删除，但是子查询可以有分布式查
## 对于delete from t1 where pk in (select pk in t2)，如果要删除的数据是跨分区的，那么分区必须必须在同一个server上，否则报错

=============================== single table delete ===============================

delete from case2_t_1 where pk1 in (1, 2);
delete from case2_t_1 where pk1 in (2, 3);

explain delete from case2_t_1 where pk1 in (2, 3);
Query Plan
=====================================================
|ID|OPERATOR               |NAME     |EST. ROWS|COST|
-----------------------------------------------------
|0 |PX COORDINATOR         |         |2        |110 |
|1 | EXCHANGE OUT DISTR    |:EX10000 |2        |110 |
|2 |  PX PARTITION ITERATOR|         |2        |110 |
|3 |   DELETE              |         |2        |110 |
|4 |    TABLE GET          |case2_t_1|2        |93  |
=====================================================

Outputs & filters: 
-------------------------------------
  0 - output(nil), filter(nil)
  1 - output(nil), filter(nil), dop=1
  2 - output(nil), filter(nil)
  3 - output(nil), filter(nil), table_columns([{case2_t_1: ({case2_t_1: (case2_t_1.pk1, case2_t_1.a1)})}])
  4 - output([case2_t_1.pk1], [case2_t_1.a1]), filter(nil), 
      access([case2_t_1.pk1], [case2_t_1.a1]), partitions(p[0-1])



// expect to be 1 plan in plan stat
select hit_count from oceanbase.V$OB_PLAN_CACHE_PLAN_STAT where statement like 'delete from case2_t_1 where pk1 in (?, ?)';
+-----------+
| hit_count |
+-----------+
|         1 |
+-----------+


