=====================================================
|ID|OPERATOR               |NAME     |EST. ROWS|COST|
-----------------------------------------------------
|0 |PX COORDINATOR         |         |1        |112 |
|1 | EXCHANGE OUT DISTR    |:EX10000 |1        |111 |
|2 |  PX PARTITION ITERATOR|         |1        |111 |
|3 |   DELETE              |         |1        |111 |
|4 |    NESTED-LOOP JOIN   |         |1        |100 |
|5 |     TABLE SCAN        |case2_t_3|1        |92  |
|6 |     TABLE GET         |case2_t_2|1        |14  |
=====================================================

